items.badge_description: It's New Brew Thursday! Drink a new beer on three Thursdays in a 30 day period! Find out how New Brew Thursday was started, and catch up on old episodes.

Your quest to quench your thirst leaves no stone unturned! That's at least 20 distinct venues!

It takes the perfect amount light, the right framing and a touch of creative love to get the perfect picture of your brew. Now it’s time to drink it! That’s 185 check-ins with a photo.
Light and crisp, a Pilsner is all you need to make your day great. Though, perhaps another one would make it even better. That’s 25 different Pilsners. Try 5 more to unlock Level 6.

Wine isn't the only beverage worthy of pairing with a delicious meal. With so many styles widely available, there’s a perfect pint for any cuisine of your choosing. That's a beer at 15 different venues categories as a Restaurant. Try 5 more for Level 4!
Does the word picking favorites mean anything to you? Obviously not. That's 10 different beers in a row.

Round and round the wheel goes! Which style you’ll be drinking, nobody knows! Your desire to explore different styles is inspiring. Keep it up! That's a check-in to at least 5 different styles. Try 5 more for Level 2!
